    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展和满足商家经营需求，京东新增部分类目商品阈值，现修订</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: black;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #3768fa; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211622812805107712\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》</span></a></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年8月18日- 2025年8月24日，规则预计于2025年8月25日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">具体新增和调整情况见下表。</span></p>\n<table style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-all; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 102.65pt; background-color: #c00000; height: 17.5pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整前后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"sc